summary: In this context, 2-methoxy-2-methylpropane and water specimen are mentioned in relation to an experimental setup involving groundwater filtration systems. However, there is no direct interaction or specific relationship discussed between the two substances. The focus is primarily on the analysis of dissolved contaminants like MTBE and benzene in the water, without elaborating on the role of 2-methoxy-2-methylpropane in this process.
